Blume
-----
A multilevel rhythmic feather designer after Philipp Blume who imagined such a tool.

Application
-----------
The most recent build of the application can be found here:
Builds/MacOSX/build/Debug/Blume.app (10.6-10.9)

Building
--------
In the Builds/MacOSX folder open the Blume.xcodeproj file, then Build the app
in Xcode.

Upgrading JUCE
--------------
To upgrade the version of JUCE, get the Introjucer tool from http://juce.com,
open up Blume.jucer, and resave the project, open it in Xcode, and rebuild.

